OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSafety plea over           
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fco-sleeping baby deaths    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffigures                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Parents are being urged to heed advice 
OL,6, on co-sleeping with babies after new   
OL,7, infant death figures were released.    
OL,9,FBBC News has learned that more than a  
OL,10,Fquarter of infant deaths investigated  
OL,11,Fin Scotland last year involved         
OL,12,Fco-sleeping.                           
OL,14,FThe NHS no longer tells parents never  
OL,15,Fto bedshare with their babies but      
OL,16,Ffocuses advice on doing so more safely.
OL,18,FThe solicitor general said the figures 
OL,19,Fsuggested some babies were dying in    
OL,20,F"high-risk" co-sleeping situations.    
